      <title>歐盟領袖將討論以色列遇襲後對伊朗的製裁</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-leaders-discuss-iran-sanctions-following-attack-israel-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[歐盟領導人將於週三舉行會議，討論在德黑蘭對以色列進行飛彈和無人機襲擊後加強對伊朗的製裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-leaders-discuss-iran-sanctions-following-attack-israel-2024-04-17/</guid>
